## Plain-English summary
- Small Evo2 scores for SNVs are expected; use them, don’t overfit them.
- Show how we measured (strategy), label the mode (standard vs massive), and cite evidence (manifest).
- Promote recommendations with gates (pathway + priors/lit), not raw Δ.

