- **Evidence Manifest Layer**: Structured, query-reproducible evidence (citations, claims, priors) tied to every recommendation; supports automated disclosure and co-inventor audit trails.
- **Massive-Mode Labeling and Governance**: Dual-mode scoring with explicit safety labeling (synthetic vs real context) and policy gates to prevent misuse in clinical inference.
- **Percentile Calibration & Gate Design**: Lightweight, disease-configurable percentile mapping and promotion criteria that convert weak S into rigorous, interpretable decisions via P/E.
- **Agentic Literature Synthesis**: PubMed → Diffbot → LLM claims extraction bound to manifest keys, enabling reusable evidence across drugs/variants with caching and TTL.

